HOW TO PLAY ?

  CREATE A GROUP:
  Create a group of 3 characters, who you select the race, the class and the
  face. Sorcerer and magician have magic powers. Mage and religious have
  others magic powers.

  SEE DOC:
     It shows you this doc !

  START GAME:
     Let's play !
     Don't forget to create a group before playing the first time, excepted
  if you're using the default one.
  Warning ! The game doesn't multitask.

  CONFIG GAME:
     It ables you to config the game in function of your machine:
    * Music On/Off : Turn on or off the music during game.
    * Window Small/Big : Switch between small or big 3D view.
    * Background On /off :Turn on or off the background (low chip memory).

  ABOUT GAME:
    Status of game, author, adress, computer model etc...

  EXIT:
      Quit game ! Returns to Workbench.

HOW TO PLAY:

  In doc:
     L.B means Left Mouse Button
     R.B means Right Mouse Botton
     Window game represents the window where the 3D mapped labyrinth appears.

  SELECT OPTIONS IN GAME:
    On the right of the screen, a left click on the word "Options" select
  options menu. Options are:
    SLEEP: Characters sleep during 8 hours. They recover all their faculties
  p.e. life, endurance, sorts.
    SAVE : Save your current game.
    LOAD : Load a saved game.
    USE  : Go to USE-SCREEN. Here, you can use some objects like food,
  determinate the sorts for sorcerer, mage etc... You can see the falcuties
  of the characters.
    EXIT : Quit game. Returns to Wb.

    1)IN ACTION SCREEN:

  * SELECT A CHARACTER:
           Click on his face with the left mouse bouton to select. You can
  see his life in red and his endurance in green. To fight you must click
  with the right mouse bouton on his hands which are holding arms. If he
  misses his punch, it writes "Manqué".

  * MOVE / ROTATE:

    Click on gadgets to move or rotate on the right of the screen with L.B.
  You can also move the mouse's pointer in the 3D window, it will become a
  pointer and you could click to move or rotate.


  * USE OBJECTS:
      On left of screen ,there is the objects list with all objects of
  selected character. You take an object with L.B in the objects list. To use
  keys, or others objects to open a door for example, you take this object
  and click with it on the door.
  To place a object or take a object in the labyrinth ,you must place your
  mouse cursor in 3D window where the labyrinth appears and click L.B. on the
  place of the object (slighty upon the object, the arrow pointer become
  different from others).
  To use magic objects, you click with R.B.
  Magic objetcs are:
  Book of sorts (Magician)
  Sphere of sorts (Sorcerer)
  Yellow or green Cross (Religious and Mage)
  If you find scrolls, you must use it in "use screen".
  You can change, exchange arms, objects between all characters, excepted the
  magic objects (unuasable by others charachters).

  * USE SORTS:
    Sorts are determinated in "USE SCREEN" (See part 2).
  The level of magic determinate the number of sorts available, so in
  beginning (in this demo version) your character has no enough magic level
  to acces at all sorts.
    Click on the magic object of your character to use sorts with R.B. There
  are 26 differents sorts divided between sorcerer, magician, religious and
  mage. The first sorts create food, phials, give more life, and the others
  are destructors sorts to fight monsters. Try them to see their effects!
    When you click on a magic object, a menu with all sorts appears:
  Click on the sort name to use it with the L.B.
  To end magic mode ,click on the item "FIN" with left mouse bouton.

  * ACTIVATE A INTERRUPTOR:

  Click on on the interruptor in window game.
  Interruptors open or close door(s) in the labyrinth.

  * OPEN A DOOR:

   In order to open a door, you must activate the interruptor or find the
  right key which open this door...

  * FIGHT MONSTERS:

    Your character must hold some arms or have sorts to fight.
  Character's dexterity determinate the delay between assaults. Click with
  R.B on the arms holding by the selected character to attack. In function of
  the character's force and his arms, his punch is more or less important.
  You can also use sorts (like Astral,Spiral..) to fight, it is usually more
  powerfull but not always.
    Monsters are intelligent, as they watch you, they approach to attack you.
  But you can meet some persons who are not aggressive...


   2) IN USE SCREEN:

    To go in use-screen, select in options menu the item "USE" or use the
  "purple" button in middle of arrows buttons.
        This screen determinate the complete description of all characters.
  To change character,click on the head's character with R.B. You can see the
  level of life, endurance, intellect, magic, etc...

  * CREATE SORTS:
  You must use magic objects (like Book of sorts, Sphere, Yellow or green
  Cross). Click on them with R.B. to attribute the sorts. A parchment appears
  which list all sorts available. To increase the sort's number, use left
  mouse bouton, or to decrease, use right mouse bouton. Points represent the
  total number of sorts available.

  * USE OBJECTS:
  To eat, take food with left bouton and click on the face of character with
  it. It's the same with all object like scrolls etc...
  Scrolls increase the magic level.
  Phials of different colors give your character more endurance, life, etc...
  Food gives your character more life.
  Clothes can't be taken and exchanged.
  When a monster is near, you coudn't affect sorts, but you can eat and have
  treatment.

  * QUIT THIS SCREEN:
  To return on action screen, click on gadget "FIN" (End).


